# Padroes Vue 3 para Componentes

## Estrutura Base (SFC)

```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref, computed } from "vue";

interface Props {
  label: string;
  variant?: "default" | "outline" | "ghost";
  disabled?: boolean;
}

const props = withDefaults(defineProps<Props>(), {
  variant: "default",
  disabled: false,
});

const emit = defineEmits<{
  click: [event: MouseEvent];
}>();

const isHovered = ref(false);

const classes = computed(() => [
  "btn",
  `btn--${props.variant}`,
  { "btn--disabled": props.disabled },
]);
</script>

<template>
  <button
    :class="classes"
    :disabled="disabled"
    @click="emit('click', $event)"
    @mouseenter="isHovered = true"
    @mouseleave="isHovered = false"
  >
    <slot />
  </button>
</template>
```

## defineProps e defineEmits

```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// Props tipadas
const props = defineProps<{
  title: string;
  count?: number;
}>();

// Emits tipados
const emit = defineEmits<{
  update: [value: string];
  close: [];
}>();

// Expose para refs de template
defineExpose({ focus: () => inputRef.value?.focus() });
</script>
```

## v-model Customizado

```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
const model = defineModel<string>({ default: "" });
</script>

<template>
  <input :value="model" @input="model = ($event.target as HTMLInputElement).value" />
</template>
```

## Slots Tipados

```vue
<template>
  <div class="card">
    <header v-if="$slots.header">
      <slot name="header" />
    </header>
    <slot :data="internalData" />
    <footer v-if="$slots.footer">
      <slot name="footer" />
    </footer>
  </div>
</template>
```

## Teleport

```vue
<template>
  <Teleport to="body">
    <div v-if="isOpen" class="modal-overlay">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <slot />
      </div>
    </div>
  </Teleport>
</template>
```

## Convencoes

- Sempre usar `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Props via `defineProps<Interface>()` com `withDefaults` quando necessario
- Emits via `defineEmits<{}>()` com tipagem completa
- Usar `defineModel` para v-model customizado
- Slots nomeados com verificacao `v-if="$slots.name"`
- Dark mode via CSS custom properties
